title: Viotrofi Piliou
description: A biological (organic) store that also carries a large variety of vegan products including veg sausage, veg burger, soya/rice/almond milk, raw materials for making ice cream, desserts, breads, cream, bread pastes, grains, fruits, washing powders, cosmetics etc. Address in Greek: ΒΙΟΤΡΟΦΗ ΠΗΛΙΟΥ 28ης Οκτωβρίου - 38.
